text: Phillip M. "Felipe" Archuleta (May 12, 1949 - December 16, 2014) was an American politician. Archuleta was a Democratic member of the New Mexico House of Representatives, serving from 2013 until his death in 2014. Archuleta died in Las Cruces, New Mexico from pneumonia, aged 65.State Rep.
